    <item>
      <title>台湾承认中国内地公民同性婚姻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/taiwan-recognizes-same-sex-marriages-involving-chinese-nationals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾表示将承认中国大陆与台湾同性婚姻，此举将使这个民主群岛上的数百对夫妇受益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/taiwan-recognizes-same-sex-marriages-involving-chinese-nationals</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 03:08:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥普拉邀请好莱坞一线明星参加市政厅活动，为哈里斯助阵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/oprah-enlists-hollywood-a-listers-for-town-hall-to-boost-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯周四在密歇根州精心制作的虚拟市政厅会议上邀请脱口秀传奇人物奥普拉·温弗瑞和一群好莱坞一线明星参加，以期聚集势头和资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/oprah-enlists-hollywood-a-listers-for-town-hall-to-boost-harris</guid>
